[[File:Swamp toad (item) detail.png|left|130px]]
A '''swamp toad''' is a small creature with removable legs. Doing so yields [[toad's legs]] in place of the swamp toad. [[Toad's legs]] heal for 3 [[Hitpoints]], are used as the tertiary ingredient in [[agility potion]]s, and the [[gnome cooking]] [[foods]]: [[Tangled toad's legs]], [[toad batta]] and [[toad crunchies]].

Collecting a swamp toad at the [[Gnome Stronghold]] is a requirement for the [[Easy Western Provinces Diary]].

The text ''"You pull the legs off the toad. Poor toad. At least they'll grow back."'' appears in the chat box after pulling the legs off.

These swamp toads cannot be used to fill [[ogre bellows]]; only [[Swamp Toad]]s found around [[Feldip Hills]] will fill them. Attempting to do so results in the chatbox message stating "''The chompy bird doesn't like this species of toad.''"

